text.tspan: Cover and cook on HIGH 15 to 20 minutes or until noodles are tender.
Serve immediately, and garnish with any leftover chopped fresh parsley.
In this diagram I illustrate instance level
representations for an ingredient and for
the role of tools in a recipe step. Class identity
for each resource vertex can be unambiguously
determined from the domain and codomains of
relationships in which they participate. I include
vertices for the Tool class and an anonymous class
to illustrate the choice of modeling non-specific tools.
The rcp namespace represents the Recipe
schema and I've used the default namespace
for instance resources. The dc namespace is
for Dublin Core properties, and I've followed
